OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloud mostly breaking up in
OL,6,Fthe morning with some warm sunny
OL,7,Fspells for most. Perhaps staying
OL,8,Fcloudier and cooler in Southern
OL,9,FAberdeenshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,12,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Perhaps some thundery showers
OL,14,Flater on Thursday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
